<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạudẖ̊kurūạ lī ạs̊ma yasūʿa
 bāṭiluⁿ kuluⁿ̃ siwāh̊
 ạis̊muhu ḥul̊wuⁿ ʿazīzuⁿ
 las̊tu ạảb̊gẖī mā ʿadāh̊

[V2]
 ạis̊muhu duh̊nuⁿ naqīuⁿ̃
 muh̊raqu ṭību sakīb̊
 yam̊lạủ ạlnãf̊sa ạn̊tiʿāsẖaⁿạ
 wah̊wa lī ạảṭ̊yabu ṭīb̊

[V3]
 ạis̊muhu bur̊juⁿ ḥaṣīnuⁿ
 makẖ̊bāuⁿ̉ min̊ kulĩ sẖar̃̊
 ạảr̊kuḍu ại̹laẙhi ḥatãy̱
 ạảḥ̊tamī min̊ kulĩ ḍar̃̊

[V4]
 ạudẖ̊kurūạ lī ạs̊ma yasūʿa
 man̊ ʿalay̱ ạl̊maẘti ạn̊taṣar̊
 wasayā̊̉tīnā sarīʿaⁿạ
 lil̊kẖalạṣi ạl̊mun̊taẓar̊</lyrics>
<title>ạdẖkrwạ ly ạsm yswʿ</title>
</song>